    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at Naukri Digital Technologies. We are on the lookout for a dedicated Frontend Developer to strengthen our Patna-based team.\n\nAbout Naukri Digital Technologies:\nNaukri Digital Technologies is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Write and execute unit tests and integration tests\n• Implement new features based on product requirements\n• Ensure code security and follow best practices for data protection\n• Optimize application performance and ensure high availability\n• Collaborate with cross-functional teams including product, design, and QA\n• Work with agile methodologies including daily stand-ups and sprint planning\n• Design, develop and maintain scalable software applications\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• CA / CMA / CFA certification\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Go\n• Proficiency in Kubernetes\n• Proficiency in Docker\n• Proficiency in Rust\n• Proficiency in Git\n• Proficiency in Agile/Scrum\n• Proficiency in TypeScript\n• Proficiency in Java\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Learning & development budget\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Patna, Bihar, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Naukri Digital Technologies!",
